  </p>

  <h3>Not Updating Organization</h3>
  <p>
    Systems need to evolve as collections grow.
  </p>

  <h3>Using It for Long-Term Storage</h3>
  <p>
    Binders are not ideal for preserving seed viability.
  </p>

  <h3>Ignoring Moisture and Temperature</h3>
